title: Pajama Pajimjams
description: Oscar pretends to be a talking pair of pajamas named "Jimjams" to make his friend Pajamas happy.

title: Bring Out Your Beast
description: Craig wants to play a popular card game, so he decides to borrow Bernard's vintage and valuable cards.

title: Welcome to Zombozo-Zone!
description: During medieval times, Team Tennyson must fight to remember that they're not in the past at all, but actually at a Renaissance-esque faire, where "King Zombozo" has hypnotized its guests into thinking they live in the past!

title: Sidekicked to the Curb
description: When Bam is sent to take on Prank, Redbird is forced to hang back because The Joker's van is too dangerous! When Bam discovers that Redbird secretly tagged along, he's upset… until Redbird bails him out of a tight spot.

title: Some Assembly Required
description: Bugs gets a new toy with assembly required and has to learn to follow instructions.

title: Za
description: Pizza's Diner needs a makeover. Apple and Onion better get this right or Pizza is ruined.

title: A Patch of Perturbed Petunias
description: Share fears she's losing her ability as a problem-solver and peacemaker when she can't calm a squabble between a group of Whiffles and a flower bed of Perturbed Petunias. Cheer discovers it's not Share's fault; the Petunias are being secretly manipulated by Bluster's rumor-mongering.

title: Haunted Campfire
description: The campers must battle ghosts of their own creation after their scary stories mysteriously come true.

title: The Library
description: The campers spend a rainy day at the library.

title: Moon Problems
description: The Moon gets sad when Oscar loses his friendship bracelet.

title: Cousin's Day
description: It's Cousin's Day- another holiday the corporations made up to make more money and Apple and Onion are going to capitalise on it.

title: The Future is Cardboard
description: The kids meet an eccentric Cardboard Creator that invites Craig to help finish his masterpiece.

title: The Curse of Elmore
description: When Gumball's schoolfriend Leslie finds an old video tape, the creepy mystery of Elmore's ghostly past unfolds. Featuring spooky and hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: Arcade Mania
description: Steven takes the Crystal Gems to Funland Arcade where Garnet learns the allure of video games.

title: Hawkodile Sensei
description: On a routine mission, Hawkodile finds some defenseless chipmunks that imprint on him.​ ​The bird bodyguard takes it upon himself to become their Sensei teach the younglings his warrior ways, but Unikitty worries his training is too intense. Will Hawkodile's "all work, no play" lifestyle push the chipmunks too far?

title: Puff Paint
description: Oscar's painting is unpopular so he goes on a journey of self-discovery.

title: Who Would Win
description: Finn and Jake challenge a giant monster, the Farm, to a fight but they end up fighting each other!

title: Pajamas Party
description: When Pajamas starts to panic that Oscar will outgrow her, Oscar tries to help but things go awry.

title: Director's Cut
description: Oscar receives a camcorder from his parents and sets out to prove to them the magic on the island is real.

title: The Potato
description: When Darwin has lunch with Idaho, he decides to stop eating potatoes in solidarity with his brotato. However, he finds his obsession with his favourite food harder to kick than he ever imagined so Gumball decides to help his friend curb his carb cravings.

title: Yes Yes Vegetables Song - Healthy Habits!
description: Baby Izzy doesn't like vegetables - until they sing a song with her!

title: The Beepers: The Visitor
description: The Beepers find the perfect groove after a new friend shreds a little too hard.

title: Catfight
description: The princesses Looma and Attea are at odds over who gets to marry Ben!

title: Time Traveling Quick Pants
description: Oscar and Hedgehog learn about a quicksand that lets them go back in time.

title: Capullos de Rosa
description: Steven recibe una visita sorpresa de algunos viejos amigos y una introducción aún más sorprendente a algunos nuevos.

title: Cosmic Bupkiss
description: A storm blocks Oscar and Hedgehog's one chance to see a comet.

title: Man of the House
description: Clarence's first night home alone spirals out of control, forcing Clarence and his pals to wage war against their own home security measures.

title: Wide Load Vacay: Dumbrella
description: Two houses, Frank and Charlie, have been traveling on the back of a truck in the rain for days. Charlie produces an umbrella to help his friend but unfortunately it's a "dumbrella" and it's looking to have some fun with them!

title: The Vampire Strikes Back
description: Ben, Rook, and Rad Dudesman come face to face with the evil Lord Transyl, a vampire-like alien who can make anyone his loyal slave! (Introducing new Ben alien, Whampire.)

title: The Bad Guy Busters
description: Izzy wants to play a superhero game and is willing to do whatever it takes to get the others to see it through.

title: Bienvenido a la Zona Zombozo
description: Durante tiempos medievales, el equipo Tennyson debe esforzarse por recordar que no están en el pasado, sino en una feria renacentista, idonde el "Rey Zombozo" ha hipnotizado a sus invitados para que crean que viven en el pasado!

title: Bee a Bee dance
description: Come sing this song and dance with our Lellobee City Farm friends to learn how to move like a Bee! Ella, Izzy, and Lettie are having fun playing and learning about bees!

title: Dog Decider
description: Unable to make tough decisions, Craig decides to put his choices in the hands of a dog named Fred.

title: Tiger Fail
description: Gwen refuses to be pressured into choosing an ice cream flavor that she does not want.

title: Elmore's Most Wanted
description: Gumball's dad has been revealed as "Elmore's Most Wanted" - but when the Chief of Police tries to investigate, things do not go according to plan. Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: What's in a Name?
description: When Cranky gets overwhelmed on a busy and blustery day at Brendam Docks, he accidentally gets Riff and Jiff's names confused, sending them on opposite deliveries. An observant Thomas hears the mistake, but does not correct the crankier-than-usual crane -- thinking, grown-ups don't make mistakes! Thomas is proven wrong, however, when he ends up at Whiff's Recycling Plant and old tires are delivered to McColl's Farm because of Cranky's error. After calming the chaos in both places, Thomas learns that it is important to speak up and tell someone they are making a mistake --- even if it is a grown-up!
originalseriesname: Thomas and Friends: All Engines Go

title: Having the Timeout of Our Lives
description: Owen forms a special bond with Duncan after having loads of fun with him during their timeouts.

title: I Am Okino
description: Inside one of the game zones, a Samurai named Okino faces a crisis of faith when he repeatedly fails to lead a series of Masters to victory, causing him to lose all hope, until some familiar ninja arrive.

title: Collect Her/Supper Villain
description: Collect Her: A fan of the Powerpuff Girls has collected every bit of Powerpuff stuff available, almost. His collection will be complete with three more items./Supper Villain: The girls' neighbor reveals he's not exactly the nice guy next door. But how will they capture him during a seemingly innocent dinner party?

title: The Hard Easy
description: A delicate race of frog people employ Finn and Jake to help them deal with Prince Huge, an evil lizard creature who's ravaging the moss swamp.

title: Dream Boat
description: Sumo devotes himself to the Sisyphean task of building a boat, defying the expectations of everyone in his life, including himself.

title: Clayton
description: Darwin needs to find a photo of Clayton to put on the cover of the school yearbook - but he makes the mistake of seeking help from Tobias, who has his eye on the cover spot himself! Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: The Brood
description: Craig's determination to get his granddad a cicada shell causes him, Kelsey and JP to become trapped in their stump!

title: One Step Forward, Two Steps Back
description: When the ninja learn that the only way to acquire the second Key-tana is by winning a dangerous race in Terra Technica they'll have to find some racing cars in unexpected ways.

title: Yo Soy Okino
description: Dentro de una de las zonas de juego, un Samurai llamado Okino se enfrenta a una crisis de fe cuando no logra que los Maestros obtengan la victoria.

title: Easter Creeps
description: It's Easter and the Tooth Fairy is trying to take over the holiday.

title: Keep Calm and Roll On
description: After Jestah's insults get the best of her, a short-tempered Bibi tries to not let the big-wheeled bully's words get to her so she can help Batgirl catch Harley.

title: Monster Visit
description: The monsters get nervous when their Godmonster comes for a visit.

title: Rose Buds
description: Steven gets a surprise visit from some old friends, and an even more surprising introduction to some new ones.

title: Rise and Shine
description: A glimpse at the wild, secret adventures Clarence undertakes each day before the rest of us, and the sun, get up.

title: Twelve Angry Hedgehogs
description: Hedgehog wants to win the Golden Science Badge but runs into some unexpected competition.

title: Sheep Bears
description: The Bears get jobs as sheep herders on an idyllic farm.

title: Voleibol
description: Steven está decidido a ayudar a la Perla original de Diamante Rosa para sanar la cicatriz en su rostro.

title: El arte de panda
description: Panda pinta un retrato de Charlie que se vuelve un éxito en su clase de arte. Pero cuando un marchante ofrece comprar la pintura, Panda tiene que lograr que Charlie se la devuelva.

title: Ocean
description: Blippi's trusty BlippiMobile safely transports him to a whole new underwater world! He dives into the sea, where he gets an ocean tour from a local resident, Jerry the Jellyfish. They swim through a huge kelp forest, explore the ocean floor and meet interesting underwater creatures along the way!

title: Panda's Art
description: Panda paints a portrait of Charlie and it's a hit with his art class. But after an art dealer offers to buy the painting, Panda has to get it back from Charlie.

title: Skips' Story
description: Walks (teenage Skips) wants to fight teenage Klorgbane.

title: Pequena Escuela Madre
description: Bienvenidos a la Pequeña Escuela Madre, un lugar en la Tierra donde Gemas de todo el universo pueden aprender a vivir juntas pacíficamente. Pero hay una Gema que se rehúsa a asistir.

title: The Awesome Brawlers and Haavik/First Fusion! Drago and Tretorous
description: The Awesome Brawlers and Haavik: It's the Haavik Show! Haavik shows up unexpectedly at the practice field and proposes he and Dan play a little game. The Awesome Brawlers have never seen this man before, but they sense something is odd about him. Regardless, when Haavik strokes Dan's ego, there's no way he's backing down from this challenge./First Fusion! Drago and Tretorous: With his back against the wall, Dan tries flipping the script on Haavik by challenging him to a game of his own - a Bakugan Brawl. If Dan wins, then Haavik will have to set him, and the other Awesome Brawler's free.

title: Stuck Up, Up and Away/Schoolhouse Rocked
description: Stuck Up, Up and Away: Bratty little Princess comes to town and wants to be a Powerpuff Girl. When she doesn't get what she wants, the girls will have to pay./Schoolhouse Rocked: The Gangreen Gang goes back to school at Pokey Oaks Kindergarten and become the school bullies. Since the girls can't fight in school, how can they stop them?

title: The XXXXX
description: Sick of Granny Jojo's ugly gifts, Nicole encourages the kids to take matters into their own hands and accidentally break her latest hideous vase. But when Gumball, Darwin and Anais try to destroy it, they discover it is more robust than it seems.

title: Arachno Romance
description: After the girls feel slighted by the Professor when he gets a new girlfriend, the girls conspire to break them up.

title: The Demon
description: Chloe and Ice Bear accidentally lose Chloe's prized hoodie to the ferocious dog next store. They go on a mission to get it back.

title: Ignition Point
description: When Finn and Jake sneak into the Fire Kingdom, they get caught in the middle of a Flame family feud.

title: The Growing Song
description: Let's celebrate everything that grows with the Growing Song! Come sing along! Have you ever noticed that everything is changing? Watch the different seasons of the year and revisit plants, animals, children, and buildings in the farm and city to see how they've grown.

title: Space Invasion
description: A visit from Puddle the alien tests the limit of Oscar's hosting skills.

title: Pepper's Blanket Is Missing
description: Pepper's blanket goes missing at a cabin sleepover.

title: Show Don't Tell
description: Ben, Gwen, and Grandpa Max arrive at a Native American national park to witness the Ayasha Plinths, an ancient Stonehenge-like rock formation. But when the sinister sorcerer Hex arrives, Ben must battle against a beast Hex magically made out of huge rocks!

title: Aparato P.L.O.T.
description: Cuando el aburrimiento en el castillo llega a niveles peligrosamente altos, la Dra. Fox convenientemente introduce su dispositivo P.L.O.T. Cuando se pulsa, este dispositivo altera la realidad para hacerla más emocionante. Richard advierte que esto puede ser peligroso, pero nadie escucha. No pasará mucho tiempo antes de que se demuestre que tiene razón y la vida en el castillo se vuelva peligrosamente emocionante.

title: Poles Apart
description: A trip to the South Pole goes upside down when Team Tennyson lands on the North Pole instead, but Ben quickly discovers the culprits: Solar & Polar Twain, magnetically-powered scientists who want to hold the world ransom by threatening to reverse Earth's magnetic poles!

title: Sarah
description: Darwin asks Sarah for a photo to put on the cover of the school yearbook. But when Sarah tries to help, things get a little sticky. Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: Fuzzy Pink Time Babies
description: Oscar and Hedgehog learn how to stop time.

title: Quien se llevo a Pan
description: Cuando Pan desaparece de la fiesta de Unikitty, ila princesa lidera una búsqueda para encontrarlo y desenmascarar al secuestrador de tostadas!

title: Mystery Boxcars
description: Kana is upset when she keeps running out of power, but a mystery scavenger hunt is just the thing to cheer her up.
originalseriesname: Thomas and Friends: All Engines Go

title: The Fair
description: The Baby Bears make a deal with a carnival worker to be prizes for a game of ball toss.

title: Wide Load Vacay: Big City Dancers
description: Two houses, Frank and Charlie, traveling on the back of a truck visit NYC where the rhythms of the city make Charlie wanna dance his little back porch off. Frank … not so much. But when you go far enough into the city, anything can happen.

title: Uncle Cupid
description: Cupid, too lonely to perform his Valentine's Day duties, comes to Uncle Grandpa for help.

title: Mop Forever
description: At Alice's dress-up party the campers are magically turned into their costumes.

title: Collect This
description: Ben finally meets the ones responsible for his intergalactic TV show, and the actor who makes Ben 10 more famous than Ben himself!

title: Onion Trade
description: A boy trade between Steven and Onion escalates to epic proportions.

title: The Sandman Is Coming
description: Daffy thinks the Sandman is a monster that throws sand in children's eyes.

title: The Cycle
description: Gumball, Darwin and Anais discover that Mr Wilson has been picking on their Dad for most of his life; ever since he humiliated Richard with a high school prank. The kids try to work Dad through it but when their efforts fail, they realize that getting back at Mr Wilson is the only way to break the cycle.

title: La Camada
description: La determinación de Craig de conseguirle a su abuelo un caparazón de cigarra hace que él, Kelsey y JP queden atrapados en su tronco.
originalseriesname: Craig of the Creek en Espanol

title: Computer Vampire
description: Oscar finds a mysterious old video game in the library.

title: Bring it On Beresford
description: On Plant-A-Tree Day on Sodor, Thomas and Diesel both want to deliver the most impressive pine for the holiday, but they'll have to compete by delivering all the other trees first. When Thomas wins the race and the pine is loaded onto his flatcar, he discovers that he overestimated the job and himself, resulting in the tree falling in a deep ditch! Luckily, Beresford the Crane has a plan to aid the Number One Engine! Will they be able to plant the biggest tree before the end of the holiday?
originalseriesname: Thomas and Friends: All Engines Go

title: Feeling Spacey
description: Oscar and Hedgehog arrive on a planet that has no emotions.

title: We Baby Bears: BHA Bha Song
description: We Baby Bears follows baby bear brothers Grizz, Panda, and Ice Bear as they journey in a magical box to fantastic different worlds in search of their perfect home.

title: Dangerous Dealings/The Hunter Returns
description: Dangerous Dealings: The Awesome Brawler's have become aware of a growing number of adults with illegal Baku-brawling devices. But where are they all coming from? Shun decides to take things into his own hands and sets up a "sting" operation to try to draw out the person selling the devices./The Hunter Returns: Lightning has been caught and locked up by an overly aggressive dog catcher! And to make things worse, he doesn't have his collar with Baku-balls. At the compound where he's being held, he runs into an old foe.  It's up to these two enemies to team up and escape their captor.

title: Rain, Rain Go Away
description: After Grumpy's anger sends his belly badge out of control with a thunderstorm that floods a newly-planted Whiffle meadow, he vows to never be grumpy again. Renaming himself "Mr. Happy," he drives everyone crazy with niceness. When the Whiffles desperately need his clouds to make rain and Mr. Happy can't deliver, Cheer and the team must get him back in touch with his inner grump.

title: Alan
description: Darwin wants to put Alan on the cover of the school yearbook - but Alan's apparent modesty gets in the way. Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: The Cake Mistake
description: Uncle Grandpa and Mr. Gus eat a cake meant for someone else.

title: Tea & Basketball
description: Sylvester wants to play tea with the girls while Lola wants to play basketball with the boys.

title: The First Day
description: Best friends Oscar and Hedgehog get dropped off at their first day at summer camp.

title: Doctor Visit
description: Uncle Grandpa hates going to the doctor but he's overdue for an important vaccination.

title: The Puppet Awesome Brawlers/The Return of Sophie
description: The Puppet Awesome Brawlers: The Awesome brawlers go to see Benton Dusk to tell him about the Fusion Bakugan and ask him if he knows anything about this character: Haavik. However, the meeting takes an unexpected twist when Haavik decides to crash it./The Return of Sophie: A video has surfaced showing Toshi using an illegal Baku-Brawling device! Shun has his hands full when Sophie starts making trouble for Kazami Holdings, accusing them of illegally exploiting Bakugan.

title: El castigo de mi vida
description: Owen forma un nexo especial con Duncan después de que ambos se divirtieran mucho durante sus castigos.

title: Esto llega hasta el Once
description: Durante una última parada en una juguetería antes del viaje inaugural de Ben, Gwen y el Abuelo Max a través del Atlántico, Ben se encuentra con su antiguo bravucón, Kevin 11, que ahora tiene nuevos poderes. Es capaz de transformarse en alienígenas al igual que Ben, como el doble "pirata" de Cannonbolt: iWreckingbolt!

title: The Phone Call
description: A threatening phone call from a stranger causes the gang to panic.

title: Rath of Con
description: Back stateside, Ben can't get into a cat cosplay competition, Top Tail, without a costume of his own; but when he goes Rath, a new cat-like alien with an attitude, Ben's newfound wild side quickly becomes much more than he bargained for.

title: Los Caza Chicos Malos
description: Izzqy quiere jugar un juego de superhéroes y está dispuesta a hacer lo que sea por ello.

title: Did Not! Did Too!
description: Bugs and Lola temporarily decide that they don't want to be friends any longer.

title: La feria
description: Los Osos bebés hacen un trato con un empleado del parque de atracciones para convertirse en premios de un juego de lanzamiento de pelota.

title: Giant Woman
description: During a mission to the Sky Spire, Steven tries to convince Amethyst and Pearl to fuse together and become a giant woman.

title: The Beepers: Funky Time
description: The Beepers play with tempo and learn that adapting to change can be…sweaty.

title: No lo digas y Hazlo
description: Ben, Gwen y el Abuelo Max llegan a un parque nacional nativo americano para conocer los plintos de Ayasha, una antigua formación rocosa parecida a la de Stonehenge. Pero cuando llega el siniestro hechicero Hex, iBen debe luchar contra una bestia que Hex hizo mágicamente con rocas enormes!

title: Popular Banana Split
description: Hedgehog and Max discover a tiny high school when they are accidentally shrunk by a science experiment.

title: Un Paso Adelante, Dos Pasos Atras
description: La única manera de que los Ninjas obtengan segunda Keytana es ganando una carrera en Tierra Technica y tiene que conseguir autos de carreras para eso.

title: Picture Perfect Park Party/Sun Block
description: Hero Celebration Day is finishing with a slideshow of everyday heroes, that is, until the projector screen rips./Pretty Big City is cooling off with an ice slide in the park, but the situation gets slippery when the slide starts melting.

title: Saca tu Bestia
description: Craig quiere jugar a un popular juego de cartas, así que decide tomar prestadas las cartas antiguas y valiosas de Bernard.
originalseriesname: Craig of the Creek en Espanol

title: Mountain
description: Blippi and TABBS head off on an icy adventure and fly up the side of Mt. Everest, the world's tallest mountain! They are joined by Betty the Yeti who is climbing to the top of the mountain in search of the ultimate snack - fresh snow!

title: Alpha Bodies
description: Cartoonito presents Alpha Bodies! It's time to use our bodies to make every letter of the alphabet, from A to Z, but one over-eager letter keeps getting ahead of itself.

title: Chocolate Money Badgers
description: Oscar learns that he can earn merit badges that unlock prizes.

title: Snow Cap
description: Pauleen Penguin hires The Looney Builders to build her a home in Looneyburg. Lola soon discovers they got the design wrong and the crew has to make adjustments.

title: Banana Joe
description: When Principal Brown sets Darwin the task of making the school yearbook, Darwin starts by asking class clown Banana Joe for a simple selfie to put on the cover. But with Banana Joe, things are never that simple. Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: Zoo
description: Clarence and Belson make a true odd couple when they're paired up during a field trip to the zoo and find themselves locked inside after hours.

title: So Many Birthdays
description: So Many Birthdays: Steven learns that the Crystal Gems are thousands of years old and decides to make up for all the thousands of birthdays they've missed.

title: Azulejo
description: Steven cuestiona los motivos de una misteriosa fusión que de repente se presenta en su casa.

title: Vote Gumball…and Penny?
description: Gumball is running for School President and is looking for a worthy running mate. When he asks his girlfriend Penny, he does not get the answer he expects. Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: Wynton's Reality Show/Bakugan Soccer
description: Wynton's Reality Show: Lia has had it with Wynton's pranking, but little does she know Wynton is in for a taste of his own medicine. A prank goes too far, and Wynton finds himself in a real-life nightmare with a rampaging Bakugan!/Bakugan Soccer: The Awesome Brawlers and their Bakugan decide to have a game of Bakugan Soccer! The intensity ramps up when Pepe, his teammates and a mysterious coach show up for a little fun. It will take major teamwork for the Awesome Brawlers Bakugan to defeat this rowdy bunch.

title: Mother's Day
description: Gumball, Darwin and Anais need to find the perfect Mother's Day gift. Will it be a cute card, a thoughtful painting or something entirely different? Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: The Soundhouse
description: Oscar and Hedgehog discover a new structure on the island and become friends with its caretaker.

title: Gravity
description: Three, two, one, lift-off! On this mission to the moon, Blippi bounces around with Rocky the Moon Rock. Light as a feather they bound up and float back down, teaching Blippi all about gravity! One small step for Blippi, one giant leap for Blippi.

title: Perfect Day
description: Ben thinks he's having 'the perfect day' only to realize he's been put in a dream world by Enoch and the Forever Knights who are after the Omnitrix. Ben's "dream world" soon becomes a nightmare world, with Ben forced to live out his ultimate terror...being stuck at school! But with Max and Gwen's help, he's able to vanquish his nightmare foes and re-enter the real world where he takes down  Enoch...only to reveal an even more powerful knight...The Forever King.

title: Wash Your Hands, Scrub That Soap
description: Ella is getting muddy. Mei comes out with a plate of dumplings, but Ella's hands are dirty!

title: I Heart Heartforde
description: Oscar, hedgehog and the other campers are excited to take a trip to the non-magical town of Heartforde.

title: El hermano de Lucy
description: Para impresionar a Lucy, Panda se ofrece a ser niñero de su hermano, Clifford. Pero Panda no puede hacerse cargo de Clifford porque el niño es demasiado caro de mantener.

title: Campers Above the Bed
description: Hedgehog finds a city underneath her bed as she looks for her missing diary.

title: Good Job
description: Falafel is starting to feel very underappreciated as the building's handyman. What's the point in all this back breaking work if not a single person will ever tell him, "Good Job"?

title: Amapolas
description: La guardabosques Tabes guía a una tropa de muchachas a una expedición en una cueva y lleva a Pardo como experto en cuevas.

title: Rainbow Race
description: Sadness levels have hit an all-time low in Frowntown. In an attempt to cheer up the citizens of the town, Unikitty and the gang load a rainbow into a tanker truck with the intention of releasing it over Frowntown. Now they must avoid the marauding Master Frown in his monster truck, to succeed.

title: Planets
description: Three, two, one, Blast Off! The BlippiMobile becomes a spacecraft on this mission to find out which planets are in the solar system! Merry the Meteor is the perfect host as Blippi is escorted through space and receives a guided tour of all the planets and their positions from the sun.

title: Una ninja justicia para Harold
description: El mundo de Harold queda de cabeza cuando sus compañeros declaran que Beth es la verdadera ninja de la clase.

title: El futuro es de Carton
description: Los niños conocen a un excéntrico Creador de Cartón que invita a Craig a ayudarlo a terminar su obra maestra.
originalseriesname: Craig of the Creek en Espanol

title: A Yoorg Awakening
description: Funshine's jokes unwittingly hurt the feelings of a strange Rock Giant. Disturbed from its slumber, the usually benign creature inadvertently creates havoc for the Whiffles until Funshine calms it by apologizing.

title: Ice Cream Headache
description: The campers get magical powers from the witches supply of magic ice cream.

title: The Rowdy Ruff Boys
description: Mojo Jojo creates the ultimate weapons against the Powerpuff Girls, boy equivalents! Enter Butch, Boomer and Brick, The Rowdyruff Boys.

title: Show de momias
description: Duncan sale en una misión para espantar a Courtney durante una excursión al museo.

title: Hello Around the World
description: Cartoonito presents Hello Around the World! All across the globe, friends greet each other in lots of different languages. Watch along and discover some of the many ways to say "Hello," around the world and beyond!

title: Puffdora's Box
description: When Blossom gets overzealous with the spring cleaning, she accidentally unleashes a group of evil spirits.

title: Perfect Moment
description: When Hawkodile admits his love for Dr. Fox, Unikitty and the gang become his love gurus to help him confess his feelings for her. Unfortunately, Unikitty's grand plans for the perfect moment of love complicates everything.

title: Convencion de Rath
description: De regreso en casa, Ben no puede inscribirse en un concurso de cosplay de gatos sin su propio disfraz. Pero cuando se convierte en Rath, un nuevo alienígena con aspecto felino y mal carácter, el lado salvaje que Ben acaba de descubrir pronto tendrá resultados inesperados.

title: The Beepers: Spotlight
description: When a spotlight gives everyone a chance to solo, a shy Beeper discovers the courage to shine.

title: Roll Chickens, Roll!/Ramp Up, Up, And Away
description: Farmer MacBarm is hosting the Sunny Field Farm Chicken Roll, but the race gets off to a slow start when the chickens don't roll./Ranger Nat can't wait to see Pinecone's Comet, that is, until his telescope falls to the bottom of a cliff.

title: CN Special: NBA All-Star Slam Dunk Contest
description: Cartoon Network's version of the NBA Slam Dunk Contest, highlighting the best slam dunks, hosted by the Teen Titans.

title: Broccoli
description: Some major construction is taking place on the roof of Apple and Onion's building and they can't get back home till it's finished.

title: Susie's Fantastical Scavenger Hunt
description: Oscar and Hedgehog must learn to exist without each other when they are put on different teams during a scavenger hunt.

title: Saxophone Come Home
description: Oscar befriends a teenage Yeti.

title: Who Took Toast
description: When Toast disappears from Unikitty's party she leads a search to find him and expose the toast-napper.

title: The Copycats
description: Gumball and Darwin are confused when they meet Kiki and Quack, a pair of siblings that copy everything they do and say. Then they find out this copycat family is making money online from imitating the Watterson family! When they fail to encourage them to find their own identity, the Wattersons realize they need a more permanent solution.

title: Perro Decisivo
description: Incapaz de tomar decisiones difíciles, Craig decide poner sus decisiones en manos de un perro llamado Fred.
originalseriesname: Craig of the Creek en Espanol

title: This One Goes to 11
description: During one last stop by a toy store before Ben, Gwen, and Grandpa Max's maiden voyage across the Atlantic, Ben runs into an old bully, Kevin 11, who now has new powers. He's able to transform into aliens just like Ben, such as the bootleg doppelganger of Cannonbolt. Wreckingbolt!

title: You Made Me
description: When a creepy sleep-peeping Lemongrab upsets Princess Bubblegum with his creepy ways, Finn and Jake need to tend to some issues in the Outer Realm.

title: Guitar of Rock
description: Mordecai and Rigby have to help Benson replace an electric guitar signed by a rock star, or Benson's fired.

title: Charmed, I'm Sure
description: Still stranded on the monster planet Anur Transyl, Ben and Rook reluctantly team up with Charmcaster to take on Zs' Skayr.

title: Guidance
description: Amethyst has been helping Little Homeschool Gems find jobs on the boardwalk, but Steven isn't sure about her approach.

title: Lucy's Brother
description: To impress Lucy Panda offers to babysit her brother, Clifford. But Clifford turns out to be too high maintenance for Panda to handle.

title: Honey
description: Blippi and FETCH shrink down and fly inside a very active beehive, where they meet Bijon, the fast-talking, fast-moving Worker Bee. With a talent for rhyming and making honey, Bijon rhymes her way through the sweet explanation of how delicious honey is made. What a very buzzy... erm...busy day!

title: The Cliffs of Hysteria
description: While being chased by Unagami's dreaded Red Visors the ninja must climb the 'Cliffs of Hysteria', however, they make a startling discovery: Unagami is converting players into energy cubes in order to build a portal into the real world!

title: Rad Monster Party
description: Ben and Rook enlist the help of intergalactic smuggler Rad Dudesman to fly them through the Anur System, the home of the monstrous aliens!

title: Rigby in the Sky with Burrito
description: Rigby wants to accomplish at least one thing he said he would accomplish before his High School reunion.

title: Tweety-Go-Round
description: Tweety leads The Looney Builders in building a new merry-go-round at the park for the kids. His crane breaks down and his small size affects his ability to contribute to the build.

title: Lost in the Sewer
description: Craig agrees to help The Sewer Queen map the sewers, but he quickly finds himself in over his head.

title: Wide Load Vacay: Eye Spy
description: Two houses, Frank and Charlie, are traveling on the back of a truck from Montana to Utah. Charlie wants to play a game of Eye Spy. He finds more and more obvious objects for Frank to spy but Frank isn't quite getting the hang of it. Yet!

title: Little Homeschool
description: Welcome to Little Homeschool, a place on earth where Gems from all over the universe can come learn how to live together peacefully! But there's one Gem who refuses to attend.

title: Saving Time
description: Mordecai and Rigby have to reset all the clocks in the park for Daylight Savings Time.

title: No Land, All Air!
description: The Bears find themselves in a world of dog fighting planes and floating airships.

title: Overnight Stop
description: Percy feels anxious about spending a night away from home during an overnight delivery with Thomas and Nia.
originalseriesname: Thomas and Friends: All Engines Go

title: Tiara Trouble
description: Bubbles' excitement over being a contestant in the Townsville Beauty, Talent and All-Around Flair pageant is ruined when Blossom and Buttercup become overbearing stage-sisters. But when a mysterious tiara causes trouble for the contestants, they realize there are bigger problems at hand.

title: Mr. Softball
description: Susie challenges the campers to a game of softball to get out of doing a chore.

title: Don't Drink the Water
description: In Florida, Ben and Max accidentally come in contact with water from The Fountain of Youth. As a result, Max transforms into a kid and Ben a toddler, with Gwen having to deal with both of them. Our trio then must track down Hex who's found the source of the fountain and prevent him from drinking the water that will make him immortal and unstoppable.

title: The Basketball Liaries
description: With the help from Basketball, Oscar makes an impressive shot that scores him a spot on the Gold League.

title: Bluebird
description: Steven questions the motives of a mysterious fusion that suddenly shows up at his house.

title: Momsoon
description: Hedgehog gets a call during her radio show from someone who needs her help.

title: Volleyball
description: Steven is determined to help Pink Diamond's original Pearl heal the scar on her face.

title: Poppy Rangers
description: Ranger Tabes leads a troop of young girls into a cave expedition, and brings Grizz as their cave expert.

title: Nothing Can Stop Us
description: Hot Dog has the audition of his life but he is missing something crucial. Apple and Onion are tasked with bringing it to him and they are adamant that nothing will stand in their way.

title: Lars and the Cool Kids
description: Steven and Lars get to hang out with the cool kids in town, but their teenage shenanigans get them into magical trouble.

title: Super Screen Cleaners
description: Thomas pretends to be a hero to help ensure the movie screen Nia's delivering arrives clean and pristine.
originalseriesname: Thomas and Friends: All Engines Go

title: A Stickier Situation
description: When Sticky Joe tries to clip his pet rat's nails, it leads to a wild adventure.

title: P.L.O.T. Device
description: When boredom levels in the castle hit dangerously high levels, Dr. Fox conveniently introduces her P.L.O.T. Device. When pressed, this device alters reality to make it more exciting. Richard warns that this might be dangerous, but no one listens. It's not long till he is proven correct and life in the castle becomes dangerously exciting.

title: Lady & Peebles
description: Princess Bubblegum and Lady Rainicorn go on a quest to find Finn and Jake who are missing after fighting the Ice King.

title: Susie Appreciation Day
description: Hedgehog and Oscar find themselves trapped in Susie's cabin and must escape undetected.

title: Momento Perfecto
description: Cuando Halcondrilo admite su amor por la Dra. Fox, Unikitty y sus amigos se convierten en sus gurús del amor para ayudarlo a confesar sus sentimientos por ella. Por desgracia, los grandes planes de Unikitty para el momento perfecto del amor lo complican todo.

title: It's My Party
description: Oscar and Hedgehog plan a surprise birthday party for Susie.

title: Tooth Fairy Tech
description: In order to earn enough money to buy a house, the Bears work as tooth fairies.

title: Just Another Manic Mojo/Mime for a Change
description: Just Another Manic Mojo: The Powerpuff Girls lose their baseball in Mojo's house, offering him the perfect opportunity to destroy these pesky superheroines if he can only get them to sit still./Mime for a Change: An accidental bleach spill turns Rainbow the Clown into the malevolent Mr. Mime. He proceeds to turn Townsville black and white and dead all over.

title: The Teen Titans Go Easter Holiday Classic
description: The Easter Bunny is missing, and it's up to the Titans to find him before Easter is ruined.

title: Carrie
description: Darwin sets out to find a photo of Carrie for the cover of the school yearbook - but they end up reminiscing about all their past spooky shenanigans. Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: Wheels on the Bus
description: Ella and Mummy take the big red bus to Lellobee farm, where she meets Mia and the rest of the team!

title: Sheep Deprivation
description: Uncle Grandpa helps a kid who can't fall asleep.

title: Puddle Eyes
description: A nap in mud seals Clarence's eyes and leaves him sightless, potentially dooming his team's chances in the school's ill-conceived "Vision Bee."

title: A Ninjustice to Harold
description: Harold's world is turned upside down when Beth becomes the class ninja.

title: The Glitch
description: In order to stop Unagami the ninja must obtain three Key-tanas, the first of which is hidden in the game zone Terra Kerana, one of Prime Empire's most dangerous game environments.

title: All Washed Up
description: Taz decides he doesn't like taking a bath.

title: Hedgehog Werewolf
description: Hedgehog gets bit by a cute puppy and is starting to act strange.

title: Ghost the Boy
description: Oscar and Hedgehog befriend a ghost who can't remember who he is.

title: Egg Hunt
description: Robin still regrets not being able to find an Easter egg when he was a kid, so the Titans head to Gotham to solve this mystery.

title: Sneeze Guard
description: Oscar and Hedgehog must work with the witches to cure Alice's camp-threatening illness.

title: Dragon Pests
description: The Bears and Squatter Otter crash a couple's swanky pad while they're out of town.

title: La Falla
description: Para detener a Unagami, los Ninjas debe obtener 3 Keytanas, la primera está escondida en Tierra Karana, uno de los entornos de juego más peligrosos.

title: Radio Silence
description: Oscar must get Hedgehog a special sandwich in order to save their friendship.

title: The Wrinklegruff Gals
description: Sick of being the tiniest kids at their new school, the girls convince Professor Utonium to create a potion to make them older! Unfortunately, when they take too much, they become senior citizens and a prime target for Mojo Jojo!

title: The Outside
description: The family goes to visit Richard's Dad. Based on his basic living standards and extended absence from Richard's life, they assume Frankie must have done a stretch in the slammer. When Frankie comes to stay with the Wattersons, they decide the way to make him comfortable is to make him uncomfortable and turn their house into a prison.

title: The Great Elf Invention Convention
description: Oscar, Max, and Hedgehog do a favor for Barb the elf in exchange for some chips.

title: Carrera de Arcoiris
description: Los niveles de tristeza han alcanzado un máximo histórico en Ciudad Frown. En un intento por animar a los ciudadanos, Unikitty y la banda cargan un arco iris en un camión cisterna, con la intención de soltarlo sobre Ciudad Frown. Ahora, para tener éxito, deben evitar a Master Frown, que merodea la zona en su camión gigantesco.

title: Oscar & Hedgehog's Melody
description: Susie holds the annual talent show that has the rest of the campers competing to win.

title: That's a Wrap
description: Duncan goes on a mission to scare Courtney during a field trip to the museum.

title: Divided We Stand
description: While at the beach, Ben discovers a new hero, Ditto, and soon has the ability to create multiple Dittos at once. These multiple Dittos can't agree on anything and drive Gwen crazy. However when the chips are down, these Dittos come together as one fighting force in order to defeat Animo and his army of replicant Stinkflies.

title: The Secret of the Omnitrix Part 2
description: In a battle with Animo, Ben in hero mode, doesn't listen to reason from Max and Gwen, and gets engulfed in a weird energy light. Little does Ben know that the "self destruct" function on the Omnitrix has just been initiated!

title: Fallo de tigre
description: Gwen se niega a que la presionen para elegir un sabor de helado que no quiere.

title: El Laberinto del Dragon Rojo
description: Aún en la zona de juego de Tierra Karana, Okino tiene que elegir entre ayudar a sus aliados ninjas, u obedecer las órdenes de su Maestro, Unagami.

title: Blue Ribbon Blues
description: When a famous scientist comes to the school, Blossom will stop at nothing to impress him at the Science Fair even if that means putting Townsville in danger!

title: The Maze of the Red Dragon
description: Still in the game zone Terra Kerana, the Samurai guide Okino has to choose between helping his allies the ninja, or obeying the evil orders of his Master, Unagami.

title: Sensei Halcondrilo
description: En una misión de rutina, Halcondrilo encuentra algunas ardillas indefensas que lo siguen como abrojos. El ave guardaespaldas decide convertirse en Sensei para enseñar a los jóvenes sus destrezas de guerrero. Pero Unikitty teme que su entrenamiento sea demasiado intenso. ¿El estilo de vida de Halcondrilo en el que todo es trabajo y no hay tiempo para el juego hará que las ardillitas sobrepasen sus límites?

title: Los Acantilados de la Histeria
description: Los Ninjas suben a los Acantilados de la histeria y descubren que Unagami convierte a los jugadores en cubos de energía para construir un portal.

title: Polos Opuestos
description: Un viaje al Polo Sur queda patas arriba cuando el equipo Tennyson aterriza en el Polo Norte. Pero Ben rápidamente descubre a los culpables: iSolar y Polar Twain, unos científicos con poder magnético que quieren chantajear al mundo amenazando con invertir los polos magnéticos de la Tierra!

title: Farewell, Phantom Thief
description: After being exposed as a phantom thief in the Bakugan battle league, the Awesome Brawlers are concerned about Ajit, but have no idea of his whereabouts. Dan is particularly affected by Ajit's disappearance and sets out to find him to get some answers./Ajit is out to set right all the wrong doings of his phantom thief past. When he attempts to break into a museum to return artifacts, his mentor Storm is waiting for him. A Bakugan brawl breaks out between two when Storm rolls out his new Bakugan: Cimoga.

title: El demonio
description: Por accidente, Chloe y Polar pierden la chaqueta con capucha que tanto quiere Chloe en las garras del feroz perro de la tienda de al lado. Se embarcan en una misión para recuperarla.

title: Ice Bear's Pet
description: Ice Bear attempts to keep a giant owl-monster secretly as a pet.

title: Uh, Oh, Dynamo
description: Worried about his little girls' safety, the Professor creates Powerpuff Dynamo, a state-of-the-art protection system, to help them in battle.

title: Waffle Cones for Whiffles
description: The Whiffles are too hot and tired to work because their daily treat, colorful ice in Waffles Cones delivered by the whimsical "Icelings," hasn't arrived - the Icelings have mysteriously disappeared. As the Care Bears search for them, Share volunteers to make the treats. It's much more than she can handle but she's determined to go-it-alone and not ask for help. Things get out of hand and Share ends up snared in Bluster's trap with the Icelings, who help her to realize that we get more done when we work together.

title: Monster Babies
description: Alice lures Oscar and his monster friends for a tea party, but only to turn the monsters into cute babies.

title: Winning A Golf Tournament Is The Solution To All Of Life's Money Problems
description: After the T-Car is towed due to outstanding parking tickets, Robin has Cyborg enter a golf tournament for the cash prize.

title: Consejos
description: Amatista ha estado ayudando a las Gemas de Pequeña Escuela Madre a encontrar trabajo, pero Steven no está seguro de su enfoque.

title: Nobody's Perfect
description: When Cheer makes some simple mistakes, she begins to lose confidence in her piloting skills and herself. The self-doubt becomes so severe, she decides to step away from her role as pilot of the Cloudseeker. But the Team needs her, the Whiffles need her, and she must regain her self-confidence so they can stop Bluster's latest nefarious scheme.

title: Ancestor Act
description: When Gumball's sister Anais researches the Watterson family tree, she uncovers a long history of nonsense. Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: Midnight Quittance
description: Ramona invites Hedgehog and Oscar to participate in a special holiday ritual.

title: Journey to the Bottom of the Crash Pit
description: The guys need to get the park video camera at the bottom of the crash pit.

title: Perdidos en la Cloaca
description: Craig acepta ayudar a la Reina de las Alcantarillas a trazar el mapa de las alcantarillas, pero rápidamente se encuentra en una situación que lo supera.
originalseriesname: Craig of the Creek en Espanol

title: The Secret of the Omnitrix Part 3
description: In a battle with Animo, Ben in hero mode, doesn't listen to reason from Max and Gwen, and gets engulfed in a weird energy light. Little does Ben know that the "self destruct" function on the Omnitrix has just been initiated!

title: Spell Crushers
description: Hedgehog tries to get over a crush so she can regain her focus on magic.
